================================================================================
Attribution and provenance
================================================================================

This project builds on the work of others, as CC BY-SA 4.0 requires it
to acknowledge.

Quotation dataset
-----------------
The quotation dataset is derived from and adapted from the
"literature-clock" project by Johannes Enevoldsen (JohannesNE), which is
also licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0:

    https://github.com/JohannesNE/literature-clock

Changes were made: quotes have been added, removed, edited, and
re-annotated (including the sfw / nsfw content ratings). Those
modifications are the responsibility of this project, not of the
original author.

Concept
-------
The underlying idea — telling the time through quotations from
literature — originated with a 2011 project at The Guardian and has been
reimplemented many times since.

